        "emailFormat": "html",
        "html": "=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <style>\n        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6; }\n        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #06b6d4); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }\n        .content { padding: 30px; }\n        .highlight-box { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; margin: 20px 0; }\n        .cta-button { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #06b6d4); color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; }\n        .calendly-button { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #10b981); color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 10px 5px; }\n        .footer { background: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }\n        .timeline { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }\n        .website-focus { background: #eff6ff; border: 2px solid #3b82f6; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 10px; }\n        .automation-focus { background: #faf5ff; border: 2px solid #a855f7; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 10px; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"header\">\n        <h1>🚀 Thanks for reaching out!</h1>\n        <p>I received your inquiry and will respond personally within 24 hours</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"content\">\n        <p>Hi {{$node[\"Webhook - Portfolio Consultation1\"].json.body.name}},</p>\n        \n        <p>Thank you for contacting me through my portfolio! I've received your inquiry about <strong>{{$node[\"Webhook - Portfolio Consultation1\"].json.body.type}}</strong>.</p>\n        \n        {{$node[\"Webhook - Portfolio Consultation1\"].json.body.type.startsWith('website') ? \n        '<div class=\"website-focus\"><h3 style=\"color: #2563eb; margin: 0 0 15px 0;\">🌐 Website Solutions</h3><p>I specialize in creating custom, mobile-first websites for local businesses. Here\\'s what you can expect:</p><ul><li><strong>Custom Design:</strong> No templates - designed specifically for your business</li><li><strong>Mobile-First:</strong> Looks great on all devices</li><li><strong>SEO-Ready:</strong> Built to help you get found on Google</li><li><strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Starting at ₱5,000 with hosting & maintenance</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://tonyfyp.com/#templates\" style=\"color: #2563eb;\">View my website portfolio →</a></p></div>' :\n        '<div class=\"automation-focus\"><h3 style=\"color: #9333ea; margin: 0 0 15px 0;\">⚡ Automation Services</h3><p>I help businesses reduce manual work through practical AI automation. Here\\'s what I can help with:</p><ul><li><strong>Workflow Automation:</strong> Connect your apps and automate repetitive tasks</li><li><strong>Lead Generation:</strong> Automated lead capture and CRM integration</li><li><strong>Reporting:</strong> Automated reports and dashboards</li><li><strong>Custom Solutions:</strong> Tailored to your specific needs</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://tonyfyp.com/#work\" style=\"color: #9333ea;\">View my automation projects →</a></p></div>'}}\n        \n        <div style=\"background: #fef2f2; border: 2px solid #ef4444; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;\">\n            <h3 style=\"color: #ef4444; margin: 0 0 15px 0;\">⚡ Want to discuss this today?</h3>\n            <p style=\"margin: 10px 0;\">Skip the wait and book a call now:</p>\n            <a href=\"https://calendly.com/tony-opusautomations/30min\" class=\"calendly-button\" style=\"color: white;\">📅 Schedule Call Now</a>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"timeline\">\n            <h3 style=\"color: #10b981; margin-top: 0;\">🎯 What happens next?</h3>\n            <ul>\n                <li><strong>Within 24 hours:</strong> I'll personally review your request</li>\n                <li><strong>Personal Response:</strong> I'll reply with relevant examples and questions</li>\n                <li><strong>Discovery Call:</strong> We'll discuss your specific needs</li>\n                <li><strong>Custom Quote:</strong> Tailored proposal with timeline and pricing</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"highlight-box\">\n            <h4 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #10b981;\">📋 Your Request Summary:</h4>\n            <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{$node[\"Webhook - Portfolio Consultation1\"].json.body.name}}</p>\n            <p><strong>Service Type:</strong> {{$node[\"Webhook - Portfolio Consultation1\"].json.body.type}}</p>\n            {{$node[\"Webhook - Portfolio Consultation1\"].json.body.message ? '<p><strong>Your Message:</strong> ' + $node[\"Webhook - Portfolio Consultation1\"].json.body.message + '</p>' : ''}}\n        </div>\n        \n        <p>Looking forward to helping you!</p>\n        \n        <p>Best regards,<br>\n        <strong>Tony Herrera</strong><br>\n        AI Automation & Web Solutions<br>\n        <a href=\"https://tonyfyp.com\" style=\"color: #10b981;\">tonyfyp.com</a> | <a href=\"mailto:tony@opusautomations.com\" style=\"color: #10b981;\">tony@opusautomations.com</a></p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"footer\">\n        <p><strong>📞 Response Timeline:</strong> Personal response within 24 hours</p>\n        <p><strong>⚡ Book immediately:</strong> <a href=\"https://calendly.com/tony-opusautomations/30min\" style=\"color: #10b981;\">Schedule your consultation</a></p>\n        <p>This is an automated acknowledgment. I'll personally respond with specific information for your request.</p>\n        <hr style=\"margin: 20px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n        <p>Tony Herrera | <a href=\"https://tonyfyp.com\" style=\"color: #10b981;\">tonyfyp.com</a></p>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
